18:36.682 --> 18:38.284
♪ ♪

18:38.317 --> 18:41.320
‐ Hey, what are you doing here?

18:41.354 --> 18:43.289
‐ I have a patient,
needs your services.

18:43.322 --> 18:44.590
‐ Listen to me.

18:44.624 --> 18:47.727
