20:36.502 --> 20:40.606
‐ Kind of.
Wait, um, heatstroke guy.

20:40.639 --> 20:43.342
‐ Yeah, but it wasn't
heatstroke.

20:43.375 --> 20:45.177
‐ How do you know?

20:45.211 --> 20:48.581
‐ Because I was there
when it happened.

20:48.614 --> 20:50.015
‐ What?

20:50.049 --> 20:51.417
♪ ♪

20:51.450 --> 20:53.385
‐ I was there.

20:53.419 --> 20:56.856
♪ ♪

20:56.889 --> 20:59.225
‐ Wow.

20:59.258 --> 21:00.326
I just...

21:01.794 --> 21:03.395
Wow.
[chuckles]

21:03.429 --> 21:06.132
Um...uh, that's intense.

21:06.165 --> 21:08.267
♪ ♪

21:08.300 --> 21:11.403
If anyone found out,
you'd get arrested.

21:11.437 --> 21:14.940
♪ ♪

21:14.974 --> 21:17.209
Why would you do that?

21:17.243 --> 21:19.311
♪ ♪

21:19.345 --> 21:23.482
‐ No, I was joking, man.

21:23.516 --> 21:26.318
I was fucking around with you.

21:26.352 --> 21:27.553
‐ Oh, okay.

21:27.586 --> 21:29.789
♪ ♪

21:29.822 --> 21:32.424
‐ You‐‐you believe me, right?

21:32.458 --> 21:34.460
‐ Uh, sure.
Yeah, of course.

21:34.493 --> 21:40.466
♪ ♪

21:40.499 --> 21:42.268
Um...

21:42.301 --> 21:43.636
♪ ♪

21:43.669 --> 21:46.639
I'm gonna get you some water
to sober up.

21:46.672 --> 21:52.411
♪ ♪

