♪ ♪

22:31.717 --> 22:34.687
‐ [grunting]

22:34.720 --> 22:41.760
♪ ♪

22:56.575 --> 22:59.478
[indistinct chatter]

22:59.511 --> 23:06.452
♪ ♪

23:11.590 --> 23:13.259
[alarms blaring]

