‐ Attention, students.

23:14.860 --> 23:18.564
Evacuate the dormitory.
Evacuate the dormitory.

23:18.597 --> 23:20.666
‐ Everybody out.
Let's go. Let's go.

23:20.699 --> 23:22.568
[blaring continues]
‐ Aw, for real?

23:22.601 --> 23:23.702
‐ Attention, students.

23:23.736 --> 23:25.571
Evacuate the dormitory.

23:25.604 --> 23:26.872
‐ Dude, let's go!

23:26.906 --> 23:29.808
‐ Single file.
Let's go.

23:30.943 --> 23:32.278
[tablet beeping]

23:32.311 --> 23:33.913
‐ It's gonna be tougher
than I thought.

23:33.946 --> 23:36.348
Might take a minute.

23:36.382 --> 23:38.851
‐ Doug, how we looking?

23:38.884 --> 23:40.519
‐ Clear on my end.

23:43.122 --> 23:45.324
[knocking]
[gasps]

23:49.561 --> 23:50.296
Hey, fellas.

23:50.329 --> 23:52.598
‐ Sir, are you a member here?

23:52.631 --> 23:54.566
‐ I'm just waiting
on some friends.

23:54.600 --> 23:56.602
‐ What friends?
‐ The Johnsons.

23:56.635 --> 23:58.070
I just got here a little early.

23:58.103 --> 23:59.371
‐ Johnsons.

23:59.405 --> 24:01.106
All right, why don't you
go ahead and come with me

24:01.140 --> 24:03.042
while you wait for them, huh?

24:03.075 --> 24:05.911
‐ Come on, there's not really
a reason for that, is there?

24:05.945 --> 24:07.313
‐ Well, I'll tell you this,
sir.

24:07.346 --> 24:08.881
You can either come with me,

24:08.914 --> 24:11.917
or I can call the police and
give them your license plate.

24:11.951 --> 24:14.453
‐ All right, I'm coming.

24:14.486 --> 24:15.888
[car door beeps]

24:17.122 --> 24:18.590
Let's see if we can get this
all sorted out.

24:18.624 --> 24:19.792
[car door slams]

24:19.825 --> 24:22.761
[tense music]

24:22.795 --> 24:25.764
♪ ♪

24:25.798 --> 24:27.466
‐ [groaning]

24:27.499 --> 24:29.535
‐ Clock's ticking, Doc.
