24:29.568 --> 24:31.403
Is he gonna make it?

24:31.437 --> 24:32.705
‐ He's gonna need
this amputated

24:32.738 --> 24:34.974
if you don't let me do my job.

24:35.007 --> 24:37.643
‐ That bedside manner
needs work, Doc.

24:37.676 --> 24:39.511
‐ [groaning]

24:39.545 --> 24:41.680
‐ Okay, he has
compartment syndrome.

24:41.714 --> 24:43.282
That's why his limb
is inflamed.

24:43.315 --> 24:46.118
Okay, I just gotta drain it.
It's nothing.

24:46.151 --> 24:48.487
‐ [groaning]

24:48.520 --> 24:49.588
‐ How did this happen?

24:49.621 --> 24:51.090
‐ Don't ask questions, Doc.

24:51.123 --> 24:52.925
♪ ♪

24:52.958 --> 24:56.128
‐ [groaning]

24:56.161 --> 24:59.798
♪ ♪

24:59.832 --> 25:00.799
