25:28.861 --> 25:30.863
‐ All right, jammer's in.

25:30.896 --> 25:35.000
♪ ♪

25:35.034 --> 25:37.036
‐ Okay, put everything back
as it was.

25:37.069 --> 25:38.404
Don't want them knowing
we were in here.

25:38.437 --> 25:39.805
They'll search
and find the device.

25:39.838 --> 25:46.612
♪ ♪

25:48.080 --> 25:49.915
‐ [whistles]

25:49.948 --> 25:53.819
♪ ♪

25:53.852 --> 25:54.953
‐ Sorry, guys.

25:54.987 --> 25:57.389
♪ ♪

25:57.423 --> 25:59.691
Must have got
the wrong golf course.

25:59.725 --> 26:00.893
Won't happen again.

26:00.926 --> 26:01.994
‐ Yeah, be sure
that it doesn't.

26:02.027 --> 26:08.834
♪ ♪

26:08.867 --> 26:15.607
‐ Shit, shit, shit, shit, shit,
shit, shit, shit, shit, shit.

26:15.641 --> 26:16.708
Shit, shit, shit.

26:16.742 --> 26:23.715
♪ ♪

26:37.629 --> 26:39.231
[gunshot]

26:39.264 --> 26:39.965
[body thuds]

26:39.998 --> 26:41.767
‐ [gasps]
‐ [grunts]

26:41.800 --> 26:43.836
♪ ♪

26:43.869 --> 26:45.704
‐ Shit, their car is gone.
Did you hear me?

26:45.737 --> 26:48.073
They're on their way back now.

26:48.107 --> 26:49.575
They're on their way back!

26:54.446 --> 26:54.847
‐ You think it was Carl?

26:56.415 --> 26:58.317
Shit.

26:58.350 --> 27:00.786
‐ Get out of there now.
They're on the move.

27:02.387 --> 27:06.458
[car engine revving,
tires squealing]

27:06.492 --> 27:08.660
♪ ♪

27:08.694 --> 27:10.395
‐ Who was it?

27:10.429 --> 27:12.231
‐ I couldn't see his face.

27:12.264 --> 27:14.166
‐ Can't see it now.

27:14.199 --> 27:20.639
♪ ♪

27:20.672 --> 27:22.741
[door creaking]

27:22.774 --> 27:29.615
♪ ♪

27:39.291 --> 27:42.227
[keypad beeps, lock clicks]

27:42.261 --> 27:45.364
[doors slamming]

27:45.397 --> 27:52.404
♪ ♪

27:53.705 --> 27:54.706
‐ What's happening?

27:54.740 --> 27:56.241
‐ They're locking us in.

27:56.275 --> 27:58.610
♪ ♪

27:58.644 --> 28:00.779
[alarms blaring]

28:00.812 --> 28:02.414
‐ Everybody out.

28:02.447 --> 28:03.515
‐ Attention, students.

28:03.549 --> 28:05.551
Evacuate the dormitory.

28:05.584 --> 28:06.785
‐ Hey, do you know
what's going on in there?

28:06.818 --> 28:08.353
‐ Some asshole pulled
the fire alarm.

28:08.387 --> 28:09.788
‐ When can we get back
in there?

28:09.821 --> 28:11.757
‐ I don't know, man.
Not soon.

28:11.790 --> 28:14.760
Apparently they gotta check
the whole building.

28:14.793 --> 28:16.795
‐ Evacuate the dormitory.

28:16.828 --> 28:19.765
[doors whirring and slamming]

28:19.798 --> 28:26.705
♪ ♪

28:30.909 --> 28:34.813
‐ Whoever's in my house,
you're not getting out alive.

28:34.846 --> 28:36.648
We're coming to get you.

28:36.682 --> 28:43.689
♪ ♪

29:06.478 --> 29:09.915
[door thuds]
[all grunting]

29:09.948 --> 29:12.251
[blow lands]

29:12.284 --> 29:13.352
‐ Moving.

29:13.385 --> 29:14.720
‐ I got high left.

29:14.753 --> 29:16.788
♪ ♪

29:16.822 --> 29:17.756
‐ Ten o'clock!

29:17.789 --> 29:21.593
[gunfire]

29:21.627 --> 29:23.795
‐ Inside!

29:23.829 --> 29:26.265
[doors slamming]
Block the door.

29:26.298 --> 29:28.300
♪ ♪

29:28.333 --> 29:29.635
Come on.
Get that.

29:29.668 --> 29:32.504
♪ ♪

29:32.537 --> 29:33.872
Get back.

29:33.905 --> 29:35.274
♪ ♪

29:35.307 --> 29:37.376
‐ Fire department
coming through.

29:37.409 --> 29:38.877
[alarms blaring]

29:38.910 --> 29:42.281
‐ Attention, students.
Evacuate the dormitory.

29:42.314 --> 29:44.716
Evacuate the dormitory.

29:44.750 --> 29:48.353
[indistinct chatter]

29:48.387 --> 29:51.523
♪ ♪

29:51.556 --> 29:54.826
Attention, students.
Evacuate the dormitory.

29:54.860 --> 29:57.029
Evacuate the dormitory.

29:57.062 --> 30:00.732
♪ ♪

30:00.766 --> 30:03.302
[both grunting]

30:03.335 --> 30:04.536
[slamming]

30:04.569 --> 30:05.804
‐ We didn't steal anything!

30:05.837 --> 30:08.040
And no one else needs
to get hurt!

30:08.073 --> 30:11.977
Lift the security
and let us go!

30:12.010 --> 30:15.314
Don't make me shoot you!
‐ Stand aside.

30:16.014 --> 30:17.416
[gunshot]

30:17.449 --> 30:19.551
‐ Damn it, how did this
go to shit so fast?

30:19.584 --> 30:22.688
[both grunting]

30:22.721 --> 30:25.557
They're not backing away.
We gotta call somebody.

30:25.590 --> 30:28.493
‐ Who the hell you gonna call?

30:28.527 --> 30:29.928
‐ Cops.

30:29.961 --> 30:31.663
‐ All right, keep it clean.

30:31.697 --> 30:33.732
I'm gonna give you this old
doxycycline prescription

30:33.765 --> 30:35.367
to prevent infection

30:35.400 --> 30:37.035
and ibuprofen for the pain.
‐ Thanks.

30:37.069 --> 30:39.671
‐ Whose van is that, babe?

30:39.705 --> 30:40.472
‐ Put your hands
above your head.

30:40.505 --> 30:42.341
‐ Hey!
‐ [gasps]

30:42.374 --> 30:43.709
‐ Put the gun down!
That's my wife!

30:43.742 --> 30:45.744
‐ Marcus?
‐ Don't be afraid, Mrs. Moore.

30:45.777 --> 30:48.080
Your husband and I had a deal.

30:48.113 --> 30:50.582
He was smart enough
to keep his end.

30:50.615 --> 30:53.585
[suspenseful music]

30:53.618 --> 30:55.520
♪ ♪

30:55.554 --> 30:57.789
I always deliver
what I promise.

30:57.823 --> 30:59.057
♪ ♪

30:59.091 --> 31:00.559
Let's go.

31:00.592 --> 31:02.027
‐ [grunts]

31:02.060 --> 31:09.034
♪ ♪

31:10.769 --> 31:12.371
‐ What the hell did you do?
[door clicks open]

31:12.404 --> 31:14.439
‐ Hey, what I had to do.

31:14.473 --> 31:15.974
They got us the name.
[door clicks shut]

31:16.007 --> 31:17.809
The person who tried
to Purge me.

31:17.843 --> 31:20.445
‐ Oh, my God.

31:20.479 --> 31:23.582
♪ ♪

31:23.615 --> 31:25.617
‐ Sam Tucker.

31:25.650 --> 31:26.618
Wait a minute.

31:26.651 --> 31:28.687
♪ ♪

31:28.720 --> 31:32.090
Sam Tucker.
Doesn't he live around here?

31:32.124 --> 31:34.526
‐ [sighs]

31:34.559 --> 31:36.128
‐ Babe.

31:36.161 --> 31:39.731
‐ [exhales sharply]
‐ Babe?

31:39.765 --> 31:41.133
What is it?

31:41.166 --> 31:42.801
♪ ♪

31:42.834 --> 31:44.436
What?

31:44.469 --> 31:50.776
♪ ♪

31:50.809 --> 31:52.611
‐ We had an affair.

31:52.644 --> 31:55.914
♪ ♪

31:59.451 --> 31:59.718
[alarms blaring]

32:02.721 --> 32:05.657
[suspenseful music]

32:05.690 --> 32:12.898
♪ ♪

32:13.999 --> 32:15.233
[door slams]

32:15.267 --> 32:16.635
‐ [whimpers]

32:16.668 --> 32:19.704
[breathing heavily]

32:19.738 --> 32:26.445
♪ ♪

32:32.617 --> 32:36.288
‐ If I could take it back,
I would.

32:36.321 --> 32:37.189
‐ Do we have any bleach?

32:39.090 --> 32:41.293
‐ Please.
‐ I said do we have any bleach?

32:41.326 --> 32:44.062
‐ Just hear me out.
I'm trying to apologize.

32:44.095 --> 32:46.498
‐ For fucking someone else
or trying to Purge me?

32:46.531 --> 32:48.400
‐ I didn't!

32:48.433 --> 32:52.337
Marcus, I had no idea
he would do anything like that.

32:52.370 --> 32:53.438
‐ Yeah?
You sure?

32:53.472 --> 32:54.306
'Cause you were out of the bed

32:54.339 --> 32:56.508
before the assassin broke in.

32:56.541 --> 32:57.642
‐ Babe, no!

32:59.377 --> 33:02.681
I didn't know about it.
I swear to you!

33:02.714 --> 33:05.350
Sam and I, we‐‐we haven't
talked in a long time.

33:05.383 --> 33:07.152
‐ How long?

33:07.185 --> 33:09.087
‐ I broke it off last summer.

33:09.120 --> 33:12.090
‐ Yeah, you did.
‐ Yes!

33:12.123 --> 33:15.594
I don't wanna be with Sam.
I wanna be with you.

33:15.627 --> 33:18.263
‐ Well, you got a funny way
of showing it.

33:19.664 --> 33:21.766
‐ I was lonely, okay?

33:21.800 --> 33:24.302
‐ Well, come and talk to me.
Tell me.

33:24.336 --> 33:26.505
‐ I tried to,
but you were at work.

33:26.538 --> 33:28.440
You're always at work!

33:28.473 --> 33:30.041
‐ So what do you
want me to say?

33:30.075 --> 33:32.777
That I forgive you?
Because I don't.

33:32.811 --> 33:33.945
‐ I thought you'd
never find out.

33:33.979 --> 33:35.614
I‐‐I hoped you wouldn't.

33:35.647 --> 33:37.282
‐ That's what's even more
fucked up.

33:37.315 --> 33:39.284
You were gonna keep this
to yourself?

33:39.317 --> 33:41.186
Even after the last Purge?

33:41.219 --> 33:45.390
Babe, I could have died,
and you weren't gonna tell me?

33:45.423 --> 33:49.227
‐ I don't wanna lose you.
‐ Lose me, Michelle?

33:49.261 --> 33:52.163
I can get Purged
because of what you did.

33:57.302 --> 33:59.337
‐ So there's been no indication
that they've spotted you

33:59.371 --> 34:01.339
in the system, right?

34:01.373 --> 34:03.074
‐ Look, they have people
whose only job

34:03.108 --> 34:04.576
is to detect intrusions.

34:04.609 --> 34:06.311
We just have to hope
that I'm better at hiding

34:06.344 --> 34:07.712
than they are at seeking.

34:09.114 --> 34:10.515
‐ Okay.

34:14.553 --> 34:19.391
♪ ♪

34:24.596 --> 34:26.731
♪ ♪

34:44.482 --> 34:47.586
♪ ♪

34:47.619 --> 34:49.788
She ran away
because of what you did.

34:49.821 --> 34:51.556
♪ ♪

34:51.590 --> 34:54.025
You ruined her life.

34:55.393 --> 34:57.228
[siren blaring]

34:57.262 --> 34:58.863
‐ Esme.

34:58.897 --> 35:00.365
Esmeralda.

