[speaking Spanish]

35:08.440 --> 35:11.309
‐ [speaking Spanish]

35:17.916 --> 35:21.720
‐ [speaking Spanish]

35:27.759 --> 35:30.095
‐ Esmeralda!
[speaking Spanish]

35:30.128 --> 35:33.431
