35:43.308 --> 35:45.176
[banging on door]

35:45.210 --> 35:50.215
[speaking Spanish]

35:51.449 --> 35:55.253
[banging on door]

35:55.286 --> 35:57.255
‐ Okay.

35:57.288 --> 35:59.357
‐ [speaking Spanish]
Esmeralda!

35:59.391 --> 36:01.259
[engine revving]

36:01.292 --> 36:04.262
[speaking Spanish]

36:04.295 --> 36:05.830
Esmeralda!
[car horn honks]

36:05.864 --> 36:09.267
[speaking Spanish]

36:11.069 --> 36:12.637
‐ [laughing]

36:12.671 --> 36:14.272
Ah.

36:14.305 --> 36:17.042
‐ No, no, no!
Esmeralda!

36:17.075 --> 36:20.512
[speaking Spanish]

36:20.545 --> 36:23.148
‐ Looks like someone
don't love you, old man.

36:23.181 --> 36:24.683
‐ Esmeralda!

36:24.716 --> 36:27.352
[shouting]

36:29.354 --> 36:30.455
Esmeralda!

36:30.488 --> 36:32.657
‐ That's okay.
‐ No!

36:32.691 --> 36:34.626
‐ We love you!
‐ [laughs]

36:34.659 --> 36:37.896
‐ [screams]
No, no.

36:37.929 --> 36:40.465
No, por favor!

36:40.498 --> 36:43.601
No, no, no!
‐ [laughs]

36:43.635 --> 36:45.470
[banging]
No!

36:45.503 --> 36:48.840
‐ [grunts]
‐ No!

36:48.873 --> 36:51.409
‐ [laughs]
‐ [grunts]

36:51.443 --> 36:57.382
♪ ♪

37:02.320 --> 37:03.388
‐ We would like to come down to
the station and press charges.

37:05.156 --> 37:07.992
‐ Your statement is fine
for now, Mr. Barker.

37:08.026 --> 37:09.728
We'll be in touch
if we need more.

37:09.761 --> 37:11.062
‐ Thank you.

37:11.096 --> 37:12.263
‐ Let's go.
[indistinct radio chatter]

37:12.297 --> 37:13.998
‐ [grunting]

37:14.032 --> 37:17.035
[tense music]

37:17.068 --> 37:18.670
[car door slams]

37:18.703 --> 37:20.739
[car engine revving]

37:20.772 --> 37:27.979
♪ ♪

37:47.732 --> 37:50.101
‐ This is how we die,
isn't it?

37:50.135 --> 37:56.641
♪ ♪

38:11.189 --> 38:14.292
‐ Grant.
Williams.

38:14.325 --> 38:16.161
Long time, no see.

38:16.194 --> 38:19.097
‐ What the hell, Ryan?
You called her?

38:19.130 --> 38:20.064
‐ You're in a lot of trouble.

38:20.098 --> 38:22.667
Breaking and entering,
attempted larceny?

38:22.700 --> 38:24.335
I'm your savior here.

38:24.369 --> 38:26.504
Finally realized
we can help each other.

38:26.538 --> 38:28.173
‐ How's that supposed to work?

38:28.206 --> 38:30.308
‐ You cut me into whatever
you're planning.

38:30.341 --> 38:33.211
Must be worth a lot
to warrant today's risk.

38:33.244 --> 38:35.780
Or I take you both in
right now.

38:35.814 --> 38:37.649
‐ Let them go!
‐ Hey, freeze!

38:37.682 --> 38:39.951
‐ Right now!
‐ Put the gun down!

38:39.984 --> 38:41.653
‐ Doug, put the gun down.

38:41.686 --> 38:43.488
‐ What?
‐ You heard me.

38:43.521 --> 38:45.190
♪ ♪

38:45.223 --> 38:46.491
I called her.

38:46.524 --> 38:47.725
♪ ♪

38:47.759 --> 38:49.260
Stand down.

38:49.294 --> 38:55.266
♪ ♪

38:55.300 --> 38:56.768
You have a deal.

38:56.801 --> 38:59.804
♪ ♪

38:59.838 --> 39:00.772
‐ Let him go.

39:00.805 --> 39:03.141
‐ Copy.

39:03.174 --> 39:04.876
♪ ♪

39:04.909 --> 39:06.177
‐ From now on,

39:06.211 --> 39:10.348
you don't make a fucking move
without running it by me first.

39:10.381 --> 39:12.116
♪ ♪

39:12.150 --> 39:14.385
I'll be in touch.

39:14.419 --> 39:19.390
♪ ♪

39:19.424 --> 39:20.558
[car door slams]

39:20.592 --> 39:21.860
[keyboard clicking]

39:21.893 --> 39:23.561
‐ So, uh,
did you take this job

39:23.595 --> 39:25.230
so you could infiltrate
the system?

39:25.263 --> 39:28.600
‐ Uh, nope.

39:28.633 --> 39:31.836
I actually believed
in what I was doing.

39:33.238 --> 39:35.106
‐ Spying on innocent citizens?

39:36.174 --> 39:39.077
‐ In order to keep them safe.

39:39.110 --> 39:41.412
Or so I thought.
[scoffs]

39:41.446 --> 39:42.547
‐ Look, I don't think
I can go any further

39:42.580 --> 39:44.716
without triggering an alert.

39:44.749 --> 39:45.950
‐ What do you mean?

39:45.984 --> 39:47.085
There must be another way.

39:47.118 --> 39:50.388
‐ Maybe if I could get some
direct link into the system,

39:50.421 --> 39:52.223
but I'd need you inside
the building for that.

39:52.257 --> 39:53.491
It's too risky
to try off‐Purge.

39:53.524 --> 39:55.126
‐ No.

39:55.159 --> 39:57.195
No, we cannot wait that long.

39:59.931 --> 40:02.901
[static buzzing]

40:02.934 --> 40:04.736
[tense music]

40:04.769 --> 40:06.170
My phone is off.

40:06.204 --> 40:08.306
Let me handle this.

40:08.339 --> 40:14.946
♪ ♪

40:14.979 --> 40:17.615
[static buzzing]

40:17.649 --> 40:24.656
♪ ♪

40:48.646 --> 40:53.818
♪ ♪

40:53.851 --> 40:56.287
‐ [gasping]

40:56.321 --> 40:59.857
‐ Attention, all students
may return to their dorms.

40:59.891 --> 41:02.427
The building is now safe.

41:02.460 --> 41:08.466
♪ ♪

41:08.499 --> 41:11.803
‐ [breathing heavily]

41:11.836 --> 41:18.843
♪ ♪

41:30.722 --> 41:32.557
‐ Going down.

41:32.590 --> 41:39.630
♪ ♪

41:46.270 --> 41:47.338
[elevator bell dings]

41:47.372 --> 41:51.042
♪ ♪

41:51.075 --> 41:54.245
[all screaming]
